name: I Find Your Lack Of Faith Disturbing (V)
Lore: 'Darth Vader ruthlessly used the Force to strike down enemies and soldiers who displeased him. He could choke victims from afar without touching them.',
Text: 'Plays on table. Unless Deep Hatred on table, opponent may use only one combat card per turn. While opponent has two Jedi on Naboo, you lose no more than 2 Force to Force drains at opponent''s Naboo sites. We''ll Handle This may target only droids and spies.',
